  "keyFeatures": [
    "Browse and search mod catalog with thumbnails and descriptions",
    "One-click mod installation and uninstallation",
    "Automatic dependency resolution and management",
    "Backup and restore mod configurations",
    "Curated mod collections for easy setup",
    "Discord Rich Presence integration",
    "Lovely mod loader integration and updates",
